sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant Controller as StaffQueuesController
    participant DB as Database
    participant View as JSP

    User->>Browser: Open /staff/queues
    Browser->>Controller: GET /staff/queues?action=list
    Controller->>DB: getQueueTicketsByClinicAndDate(user.clinicId, today)
    Controller->>DB: Load patients, services, clinicServices
    Controller->>View: Forward /WEB-INF/staff/queues/list.jsp
    View-->>Browser: Live queue view

    User->>Browser: Call next patient
    Browser->>Controller: POST /staff/queues?action=call
    Controller->>DB: updateQueueTicket(status=CALLED)
    Controller->>DB: createQueueTicketNotification(ticket)
    Controller-->>Browser: 204 No Content

    User->>Browser: Complete queue ticket
    Browser->>Controller: POST /staff/queues?action=complete
    Controller->>DB: updateQueueTicket(status=COMPLETED)
    Controller->>DB: removeNotificationOnUpdate(ticket)
    Controller-->>Browser: 204 No Content

    User->>Browser: Skip queue ticket
    Browser->>Controller: POST /staff/queues?action=skip
    Controller->>DB: updateQueueTicket(status=SKIPPED)
    Controller->>DB: removeNotificationOnUpdate(ticket)
    Controller->>DB: createQueueTicketNotification(ticket)
    Controller-->>Browser: 204 No Content
